Thanx to everyone who submitted their chars through the form as 
asked. As for everyone who SENT ME THEIRS OVER EMAIL like NOT asked, 
assassins will be arriving at your houses shortly.. Kidding. But 
please submit your character profiles through the form.

Kinger, please use your char's full name (Proto1000) instead of just 
Proto, cause I have a bot named Proto as well.

::FZ/Kluster/Repressor/Lavacons/Perndabot/Proto::

FZ smiles, watching Kluster exit the Cybertronian Fire and open fire 
on Dark One.

"Alliance bots," he says over his comm, "Capture the bot that has 
just emerged out of the Cybertronian Fire. I want him alive."

FZ fires two more missiles into the shields of the Cybertronian Fire, 
watching Astral and Griplash fly toward the commander of the 
Cybertronian Fire.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Repressor's systems come back online, the bot instantly jumping up. 
He sees an explosion as the grenade that Shocker had put in 
Demolition goes off.

"Slag!" He swears to himself, running up to Demolition and looking at 
the bot. All he needed to do was recover one thing, and a clone would 
be possible.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Perndabot smashes a fist into Proto's face as the two bots roll over 
the ground, trying to kill each other.
